(INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS)

1145
01:11:40,838 --> 01:11:42,714
Didn't Linda say she'd be
here for final rehearsal?

1146
01:11:42,799 --> 01:11:46,218
Oh, relax, our audiences
aren't professional critics.

1147
