1183
01:14:32,218 --> 01:14:34,803
<i>♪ Don't need ♪
♪ any long speeches ♪</i>

1184
01:14:34,887 --> 01:14:36,763
<i>♪ Or shouts of "Hooray!" ♪</i>

1185
01:14:37,098 --> 01:14:41,893
<i>♪ No words can say as much ♪
♪ as firecrackers can say ♪</i>

1186
01:14:47,358 --> 01:14:52,612
<i>♪ Freedom! Freedom! ♪</i>

1187
01:14:52,697 --> 01:14:57,200
<i>♪ Here comes the Freedom Man ♪</i>

1188
01:14:57,285 --> 01:14:59,995
<i>♪ On this day ♪
♪ of independence ♪</i>

